Definition.WordDefinition: unresolved adj 1: not solved; "many crimes remain unsolved"; "many problems remain unresolved" [syn: {unsolved}] [ant: {solved}] 2: not brought to a conclusion; subject to further thought; "an open question"; "our position on this bill is still undecided"; "our lawsuit is still undetermined" [syn: {open}, {undecided}, {undetermined}] 3: characterized by musical dissonance; harmonically unresolved [syn: {dissonant}]
